        "approved_only": true,
        "description": "Only the approved gradient set may be used — never invent gradients. Approved gradients: Brand Blue → Dark Navy (#00529b → #011E45) for dark backgrounds/blue masthead/waves; Sky Blue → Deep Blue (#358CCB → #003D74) for blue backgrounds/waves; Sunshine → 75% Gold (#faa31b → Gold @75%) for warm backgrounds; Golden Sand → White → Light Blue (#FEF1C8 → #ffffff → #E6F0F9) for soft light backgrounds; Golden Sand → 75% Gold → Sunshine (#FEF1C8 → Gold @75% → #faa31b) for warm light-to-saturated backgrounds. Used as backgrounds, in combination with the wave graphic, and with the LISRAYA logo mark. Approved values only."
      },
